PSXDataSet.name: casSupport
PSXDataSet.description: This is authtype dispatcher resource. This resource never needs to be touched. sys_casAuthtypeDispatcher post exit attached to this resource finds appropriate authtype implementaion resource from the config file (Authtypes.properties), makes an internal request an then return the merged result document.

PSXDataSelector.nativeStatement: SELECT CONTENTSTATUS.CONTENTID, PSX_TEMPLATE.ASSEMBLYURL, PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.DEPENDENT_ID, PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.VARIANT_ID, CONTENTSTATUS.CURRENTREVISION, PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.RID, PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.SLOT_ID, PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.DEPENDENT_ID AS itemcontentid1 , PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.VARIANT_ID AS variantid1 , PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.RID AS sysid1 , RXSLOTTYPE.SLOTNAME, PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.SORT_RANK, PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.SITE_ID, PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.FOLDER_ID FROM CONTENTSTATUS CONTENTSTATUS, PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP, PSX_TEMPLATE PSX_TEMPLATE, STATES STATES, RXSLOTTYPE RXSLOTTYPE WHERE CONTENTSTATUS.CONTENTID = PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.DEPENDENT_ID AND PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.VARIANT_ID = PSX_TEMPLATE.TEMPLATE_ID AND CONTENTSTATUS.CONTENTSTATEID = STATES.STATEID AND PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.SLOT_ID = RXSLOTTYPE.SLOTID AND CONTENTSTATUS.WORKFLOWAPPID = STATES.WORKFLOWAPPID AND PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.OWNER_ID = :"PSXSingleParam/sys_contentid" AND PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.OWNER_REVISION = :"PSXSingleParam/sys_revision" AND (STATES.CONTENTVALID = 'y' OR STATES.CONTENTVALID = 'i') ORDER BY PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.SORT_RANK ASC

SELECT CONTENTSTATUS.CONTENTID, PSX_TEMPLATE.ASSEMBLYURL, PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.DEPENDENT_ID, PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.VARIANT_ID, PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.SITE_ID, PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.FOLDER_ID, CONTENTSTATUS.CURRENTREVISION, PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.RID, PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.SLOT_ID, PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.DEPENDENT_ID AS itemcontentid1 , PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.VARIANT_ID AS variantid1 , PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.RID AS sysid1 , RXSLOTTYPE.SLOTNAME, PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.SORT_RANK FROM CONTENTSTATUS CONTENTSTATUS, PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP, PSX_TEMPLATE PSX_TEMPLATE, STATES STATES, RXSLOTTYPE RXSLOTTYPE WHERE CONTENTSTATUS.CONTENTID = PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.DEPENDENT_ID AND PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.VARIANT_ID = PSX_TEMPLATE.TEMPLATE_ID AND CONTENTSTATUS.CONTENTSTATEID = STATES.STATEID AND PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.SLOT_ID = RXSLOTTYPE.SLOTID AND CONTENTSTATUS.WORKFLOWAPPID = STATES.WORKFLOWAPPID AND PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.OWNER_ID = :"PSXSingleParam/sys_contentid" AND PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.OWNER_REVISION = :"PSXSingleParam/sys_revision" AND (STATES.CONTENTVALID = 'y' OR STATES.CONTENTVALID = 'i') ORDER BY PSX_OBJECTRELATIONSHIP.SORT_RANK ASC
